Package sokochan.GridObjects

A package containing all the objects that can be placed on a SokochanGrid Created by Vittorio on 23-Nov-16.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Crate
    Represent a crate in the SokochanGrid.
    Diamond
    Extends Tile, and represents the position in the grid where the crates should be taken to.
    GridObject
    This abstract class aims to provide methods and fields for every kind of object placed in a SokochanGrid (both tiles and movable objects).
    MovableGridObject
    Another abstract class, that will provide methods for moving GridObjects.
    Tile
    A Tile represents the normal "floor" of the grid, and can be walked upon, if it is empty.
    TileGridObject
    An abstract class for a tile, i.e.
    Wall
    A Tile child that is always non-walkable.
    WarehouseKeeper
    Extends from MovableGridObject and allows movement of the player.
